@startuml
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Ca sử dụng quên mật khẩu

actor "Khách hàng" as User
boundary "_ForgotPasswordScreenState" as ForgotPasswordScreenState
boundary "_VerifyOtpScreenState" as VerifyOtpScreenState
boundary "_RecoverPasswordScreenState" as RecoverPasswordScreenState
control "AuthApiService" as AuthApiService
control "AuthController" as AuthController
control "AuthServiceImpl" as AuthServiceImpl
database "UserRepository" as UserRepository
control "OtpCodeUtil" as OtpCodeUtil
database "RedisTemplate" as RedisTemplate
control "EmailUtil" as EmailUtil
control "JavaMailSender" as JavaMailSender
control "JwtUtil" as JwtUtil
control "UserMapper" as UserMapper
control "SecurityContextHolder" as SecurityContextHolder
control "PasswordEncoder" as PasswordEncoder
control "Navigator" as Navigator

User -> ForgotPasswordScreenState: 1: nhập email và bấm Đặt lại mật khẩu
activate ForgotPasswordScreenState

ForgotPasswordScreenState -> ForgotPasswordScreenState: 2: _submitForgotPassword()
activate ForgotPasswordScreenState

ForgotPasswordScreenState -> AuthApiService: 3: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 4: forgotPassword(OtpRequest)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> AuthController: 5: gọi API POST /auth/forgot-password
activate AuthController
AuthController -> AuthController: 6: forgotPassword(OtpRequest)
activate AuthController

AuthController -> AuthServiceImpl: 7: gọi
activate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl -> AuthServiceImpl: 8: forgotPassword(OtpRequest)
activate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> UserRepository: 9: gọi
activate UserRepository
UserRepository -> UserRepository: 10: existsByEmailAndActive(email, true)
activate UserRepository
deactivate UserRepository
UserRepository --> AuthServiceImpl: 11: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserRepository

AuthServiceImpl -> OtpCodeUtil: 12: gọi
activate OtpCodeUtil
OtpCodeUtil -> OtpCodeUtil: 13: generateOtpCode()
activate OtpCodeUtil
deactivate OtpCodeUtil
OtpCodeUtil --> AuthServiceImpl: 14: trả về kết quả
deactivate OtpCodeUtil

AuthServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 15: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 16: opsForValue().set(email, otp, 5, TimeUnit.MINUTES)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> AuthServiceImpl: 17: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

AuthServiceImpl -> EmailUtil: 18: gọi
activate EmailUtil
EmailUtil -> EmailUtil: 19: sendOtpEmail(email, otp, title, message, 5)
activate EmailUtil

EmailUtil -> JavaMailSender: 20: gọi
activate JavaMailSender
JavaMailSender -> JavaMailSender: 21: send(mimeMessage)
activate JavaMailSender
deactivate JavaMailSender
JavaMailSender --> EmailUtil: 22: trả về kết quả
deactivate JavaMailSender

deactivate EmailUtil
EmailUtil --> AuthServiceImpl: 23: trả về kết quả
deactivate EmailUtil

deactivate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl --> AuthController: 24: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthServiceImpl

deactivate AuthController
AuthController --> AuthApiService: 25: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> ForgotPasswordScreenState: 26: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

ForgotPasswordScreenState -> Navigator: 27: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 28: pushNamed(AppRoutes.verifyOtp, VerifyOtpArgs)
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> ForgotPasswordScreenState: 29: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate ForgotPasswordScreenState

ForgotPasswordScreenState --> User: 30: điều hướng đến màn hình nhập OTP
deactivate ForgotPasswordScreenState

User -> VerifyOtpScreenState: 31: nhập OTP và bấm Xác thực
activate VerifyOtpScreenState

VerifyOtpScreenState -> VerifyOtpScreenState: 32: _submitOtp(VerifyOtpArgs)
activate VerifyOtpScreenState

VerifyOtpScreenState -> AuthApiService: 33: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 34: verifyOtp(VerifyOtpRequest)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> AuthController: 35: gọi API POST /auth/otp/verify
activate AuthController
AuthController -> AuthController: 36: verifyOtp(VerifyOtpRequest)
activate AuthController

AuthController -> AuthServiceImpl: 37: gọi
activate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl -> AuthServiceImpl: 38: verifyOtp(VerifyOtpRequest)
activate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> UserRepository: 39: gọi
activate UserRepository
UserRepository -> UserRepository: 40: findByEmail(email)
activate UserRepository
deactivate UserRepository
UserRepository --> AuthServiceImpl: 41: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserRepository

AuthServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 42: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 43: opsForValue().get(email)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> AuthServiceImpl: 44: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

AuthServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 45: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 46: delete(email)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> AuthServiceImpl: 47: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

AuthServiceImpl -> JwtUtil: 48: gọi
activate JwtUtil
JwtUtil -> JwtUtil: 49: generateToken(User, OtpPurpose)
activate JwtUtil
deactivate JwtUtil
JwtUtil --> AuthServiceImpl: 50: trả về kết quả
deactivate JwtUtil

AuthServiceImpl -> UserMapper: 51: gọi
activate UserMapper
UserMapper -> UserMapper: 52: entityToResponse(User)
activate UserMapper
deactivate UserMapper
UserMapper --> AuthServiceImpl: 53: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserMapper

deactivate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl --> AuthController: 54: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthServiceImpl

deactivate AuthController
AuthController --> AuthApiService: 55: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> VerifyOtpScreenState: 56: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

VerifyOtpScreenState -> Navigator: 57: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 58: pushReplacementNamed(AppRoutes.recoverPassword, RecoverPasswordArgs)
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> VerifyOtpScreenState: 59: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate VerifyOtpScreenState

VerifyOtpScreenState --> User: 60: điều hướng đến màn hình tạo mật khẩu mới
deactivate VerifyOtpScreenState

User -> RecoverPasswordScreenState: 61: nhập mật khẩu mới và bấm Đặt lại mật khẩu
activate RecoverPasswordScreenState

RecoverPasswordScreenState -> RecoverPasswordScreenState: 62: _submit(RecoverPasswordArgs)
activate RecoverPasswordScreenState

RecoverPasswordScreenState -> AuthApiService: 63: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 64: resetPassword(token, ResetPasswordRequest)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> AuthController: 65: gọi API POST /auth/reset-password
activate AuthController
AuthController -> AuthController: 66: resetPassword(token, ResetPasswordRequest)
activate AuthController

AuthController -> AuthServiceImpl: 67: gọi
activate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl -> AuthServiceImpl: 68: resetPassword(ResetPasswordRequest, token)
activate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> SecurityContextHolder: 69: gọi
activate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder -> SecurityContextHolder: 70: getContext().getAuthentication().getName()
activate SecurityContextHolder
deactivate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder --> AuthServiceImpl: 71: trả về kết quả
deactivate SecurityContextHolder

AuthServiceImpl -> UserRepository: 72: gọi
activate UserRepository
UserRepository -> UserRepository: 73: findByEmailAndActive(email, true)
activate UserRepository
deactivate UserRepository
UserRepository --> AuthServiceImpl: 74: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserRepository

AuthServiceImpl -> PasswordEncoder: 75: gọi
activate PasswordEncoder
PasswordEncoder -> PasswordEncoder: 76: encode(password)
activate PasswordEncoder
deactivate PasswordEncoder
PasswordEncoder --> AuthServiceImpl: 77: trả về kết quả
deactivate PasswordEncoder

AuthServiceImpl -> JwtUtil: 78: gọi
activate JwtUtil
JwtUtil -> JwtUtil: 79: getClaims(token)
activate JwtUtil
deactivate JwtUtil
JwtUtil --> AuthServiceImpl: 80: trả về kết quả
deactivate JwtUtil

AuthServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 81: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 82: opsForValue().set(claims.id, token, ttl)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> AuthServiceImpl: 83: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

deactivate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl --> AuthController: 84: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthServiceImpl

deactivate AuthController
AuthController --> AuthApiService: 85: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> RecoverPasswordScreenState: 86: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

RecoverPasswordScreenState -> Navigator: 87: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 88: pushNamedAndRemoveUntil(AppRoutes.login)
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> RecoverPasswordScreenState: 89: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate RecoverPasswordScreenState

RecoverPasswordScreenState --> User: 90: điều hướng về màn hình đăng nhập
deactivate RecoverPasswordScreenState

@enduml
